==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: coattails
<hw>coattails</hw> <pos>n. pl.</pos> <mark>[fig.]</mark> <def>the
influence of another person; the effect of association with another
person; <as>as, he was elected to office on the president's
<ex>coattails</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>on the coattails of</b></col> <sd>(a)</sd> <cd>helped by
association with another person. See <er>coattails</er>.</cd>
<sd>(b)</sd> <cd>caused by, or immediately following (an
event).</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

